headline: IQVIA Announces Strategic Collaboration with AWS, Naming AWS as Preferred Agentic Cloud Provider to Power Next-Generation AI Platform
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., December 02, 2025--IQVIA (NYSE: IQV), a leading global provider of clinical research services, commercial insights and healthcare intelligence to the life sciences and healthcare industries, today announced a strategic collaboration with Amazon Web Services (AWS), naming AWS as IQVIA’s Preferred Agentic Cloud Provider.
